com.jdon.controller.model
类 PageIterator

java.lang.Object
  com.jdon.controller.model.PageIterator
所有已实现的接口：
java.io.Serializable, java.util.Iterator
public class PageIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator, java.io.Serializable

All model's primary key(or identifier) collection of every page that will be displayed it carry the model's primary key collection from persistence lay to presentation lay . restriction : the class type pf your model primary key must be equal to the data type of primary key of the table. com.jdon.model.query.PageIteratorSolver supply a factory that create this class in persistence lay the class is stateful.

版本：
1.4
另请参见：
ModelListForm PageIteratorSolver, 序列化表格

PageIterator

public PageIterator(int allCount,
                    java.lang.Object[] keys,
                    int startIndex,
                    int endIndex,

Block Construtor default construtor, this is a block construtor the keys's lengt is always greater than the page length that will be displayed.

参数：
allCount - the all count for all results.
keys - primary keys collection for every block
start - the start index in the keys.
endIndex - the end index in the keys
actualCount - the count of the primary keys collection.

PageIterator

public PageIterator(int allCount,
                    java.lang.Object[] keys)
Page Construtor this is user customization construtor, the keys's lengt is always equals the page length that will be displayed.

参数：
allCount - all count for all results
keys - primary keys collection for a page defined by client's count value.
